T1  - Management Game Teams In Education And Organization Research: An Experiment On Risk Taking
AU  - Lewin, Arie Y.
AU  - Weber, Wesley L.
Y1  - 1969/03/01
PY  - 1969
DA  - 1969/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/254671
DO  - 10.5465/254671
